high_descs: walk around and reach the kitchen stove
pick up the pot from stove
walk around and reach the desklamp
anns.task_desc: pick up the pot from stove and turn on the desklamp

high_descs: Turn left, enter the room, take right towards the counter top.
Take the pot from the counter top.
Turn around, move forward, take left, leave the room, move straight towards the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: To take the pot from the counter top, put the desk lamp on.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right.
Pick up knife from the desk.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a knife by the light of a desk lamp.
